{"tid":1155826,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［有感而發］有冇網站係設計俾人理性討論／辯論","createTime":"2019-05-15T08:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T08:07:23.000Z","uid":30506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"de613286493788d8c9891f7b46d1852f720b8497","tid":1155826,"uid":30506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:04:02.000Z","msg":"呢兩日喺度爭拗達哥應該用英文定係簡體字<br />\n仲傾到臉紅耳赤，講晒粗口人身攻擊咁，三毛更加唔使講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我明連登係討論區，但有時候都想認真聽下對方／我方有咩論點、論據，是其是非其非，鼓勵眾user 離開低層次嘅辱罵同攻擊<br />\n<br />\n所以諗緊究竟有冇啲網站，係俾人理性傾下<br />\nset 好一啲規矩，例如唔准講粗口、唔可以人身攻擊、要有論點、限時等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d97aa79aa4b9b8c91e3d8f158b209fca155e3c1","tid":1155826,"uid":470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:05:21.000Z","msg":"冇呀戇鳩笑你洗撚擇日呀"},{"pid":"bb91ee7a4c4a632849325d6ade18e1febf1446fd","tid":1155826,"uid":30836,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/original/000/328/079/3c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Foriginal%2F000%2F328%2F079%2F3c9.jpg&h=b9249e74&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25498f25932f4afa8fab728b6776a623455f85d1","tid":1155826,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:07:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://discuss.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdiscuss.com&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV5ODbC9uMYpCHTvDpi7yeoo%3D&h=122b0c65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">discuss.com</a>"}]}